            <title>[LUDOC-469] correct description of &quot;Non Blocking Restore&quot; HSM policy</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-469</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the operations manual the description of the &quot;Non Blocking Restore&quot; HSM policy is incorrect. It reads &quot;No automatic restore is triggered. Access to a released file returns ENODATA.&quot; In fact a restore is triggered.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
